This is documentation for the [Redis service for PCF](https://network.pivotal.io/products/p-redis).

## Redis for PCF
Redis is an easy to use, high speed key-value store that can be used as a database, cache and message broker. It supports a range of data structures including strings, lists, hashes, sets, bitmaps, hyperloglogs and geospatial indexes. Redis for PCF provides metrics and logging so operators can monitor Redis health. Persistence is provided via RDB and AOF, with backups to an S3 bucket on a configurable schedule.

